.TH glu 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
glu \- Erlang wrapper functions for OpenGL

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Standard OpenGL API

.PP
This documents the functions as a brief version of the complete OpenGL reference pages.

